verbose_text: Interestingly, inflammatory KLRG1 hi ILC2s, which migrated to the lungs upon IL-25 challenge or following infection with the hookworm Nippostrongylus brasiliensis or the fungus Candida albicans, expressed both GATA3 and RORgammat and could produce IL-17 as well as IL-13 in vitro.
